<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>这位扫地的环卫工叫吴金理</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>他的左手从小臂处缺失</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>连吃饭都不方便</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>尽管如此</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>他已经从事了七年环卫工作</span></strong></span></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
